{{Infobox dungeon |name = Celestial Tower |image = [[File:Celestial Tower.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Celestial Tower. |tokens = 206,500 |location = Unova Route 7 }} '''Celestial Tower''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
